            "title": "Prompt 4",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"style_mode\": \"raw_photoreal_high_fidelity\",\n  \"look\": \"social media realism, smartphone aesthetic, UGC founder content for Meta ads\",\n  \"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16 vertical\",\n\n  \"camera\": {\n    \"vantage\": \"eye-level, direct front-facing, smartphone propped on bathroom counter\",\n    \"framing\": \"waist-up medium shot, subject occupies 55% of frame, slight off-center (rule of thirds, subject shifted slightly right)\",\n    \"lens_behavior\": \"smartphone front camera equivalent, ~24mm wide-angle with subtle barrel distortion at edges\",\n    \"sensor_quality\": \"subtle digital grain, limited dynamic range, slightly blown-out highlights near window\",\n    \"shake\": \"minimal — phone is propped, not handheld, but not tripod-perfect either\"\n  },\n\n  \"scene\": {\n    \"environment\": {\n      \"setting\": \"modern, aesthetically curated bathroom — clean and elevated but still personal. Large format white marble-look porcelain tile with subtle grey veining, floating walnut vanity with brass hardware, round backlit mirror partially visible at edge of frame, small eucalyptus sprig in a ceramic vase on the counter\",\n      \"lighting\": {\n        \"key_light\": \"natural morning sunlight from frosted bathroom window, camera-left, warm color temperature (~4500K)\",\n        \"fill\": \"ambient bounce from light marble-look tile walls, soft and even\",\n        \"quality\": \"soft directional light with gentle shadows on right side of face, no harsh contrast\",\n        \"interaction\": \"light catches the metallic surface of the electric razor, creating a subtle specular highlight on the device body\"\n      },\n      \"time_of_day\": \"morning\",\n      \"atmosphere\": \"warm, bright, intimate — the natural context where this product lives and gets used\"\n    },\n\n    \"subject\": {\n      \"obj_001\": {\n        \"type\": \"person\",\n        \"description\": \"woman, mid-to-late 20s, racially ambiguous/mixed features, clear skin with visible natural texture (pores, subtle under-eye warmth), dark brown hair pulled back in a loose low bun with messy flyaway strands framing face\",\n        \"expression\": {\n          \"mood\": \"proud and excited — she's about to show you something she built, contained enthusiasm with a confident smile forming\",\n          \"action\": \"mid-speech, mouth open as if saying the word 'Meet,' chin up slightly with pride, eyes bright and engaged\"\n        },\n        \"skin\": \"realistic skin micro-texture (pores, natural gloss on forehead and nose from morning moisture), no makeup or very minimal — bare skin with natural warmth and flush on cheeks\",\n        \"eyes\": \"clear catchlights in both eyes from window light, warm brown, engaged and direct\",\n        \"attire\": {\n          \"top\": \"plain white ribbed tank top, slightly oversized, one strap sitting loosely on shoulder — dressed for a morning routine, not for camera\",\n          \"material_fidelity\": \"soft cotton with visible ribbed texture, natural drape, no logos or patterns\"\n        },\n        \"positioning\": \"standing at bathroom counter, body angled slightly toward camera-left, face turned fully toward camera, weight on left hip — casual, not posed\"\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"product\": {\n      \"obj_002\": {\n        \"type\": \"product — electric razor\",\n        \"description\": \"Silk Glide Pro — sleek wireless women's electric razor, modern industrial design, matte rose gold / soft pink metallic body with subtle sheen, compact ergonomic form factor, micro-foil head visible at top\",\n        \"text_rendering\": \"brand name 'Silk Glide Pro' subtly embossed on the body of the device in small sans-serif lettering\",\n        \"positioning\": \"held prominently in subject's right hand at chest level, arm extended slightly toward camera — a deliberate 'meet this' presentation angle. Product is the focal point of the composition alongside her face. Fingers wrapped naturally around the handle, foil head and brand name clearly visible\",\n        \"spatial_relationship\": \"product is 10 inches from subject's body, between subject and camera, prominently placed in the lower-center-right of the frame\",\n        \"material_fidelity\": \"matte metallic body with soft specular highlight from window light, micro-foil head has fine metallic mesh texture, power button visible as small recessed circle\"\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"background\": {\n      \"description\": \"floating walnut vanity counter and edge of round backlit mirror visible behind subject, slightly out of focus (shallow depth of field simulation). Clean, curated — the kind of bathroom you'd see in a lifestyle brand's Instagram. This is where the product naturally lives\",\n      \"narrative_clutter\": [\n        \"obj_003: a frosted amber glass skincare bottle with minimalist label and pump top, partially visible at bottom-left edge of frame on the counter\",\n        \"obj_004: a neatly folded waffle-textured linen hand towel in warm off-white on the counter\",\n        \"obj_005: a small ceramic tray holding a few gold hair pins and a black hair tie\",\n        \"obj_006: a sprig of dried eucalyptus in a slim white ceramic bud vase, slightly behind the subject's elbow, out of focus\"\n      ],\n      \"depth\": \"background elements at f/2.0 equivalent blur — present but not competing with subject\"\n    }\n  },\n\n  \"aesthetic_controls\": {\n    \"render_intent\": \"amateur smartphone UGC for social media — this should look like a real woman filming herself in her bathroom while demonstrating her product, not a studio shoot\",\n    \"material_fidelity\": [\n      \"realistic skin micro-texture with visible pores and natural oil sheen\",\n      \"soft cotton ribbed tank with fabric weight and drape\",\n      \"metallic razor body with accurate specular response\",\n      \"marble-look porcelain tile with subtle grey veining and clean grout lines\",\n      \"natural hair texture with flyaways and loose strands\"\n    ],\n    \"degradation\": {\n      \"grain\": \"subtle luminance noise consistent with smartphone sensor in indoor natural light\",\n      \"highlights\": \"slightly blown highlights on the window-side of face and on marble-look tile behind subject\",\n      \"dynamic_range\": \"limited — shadows slightly lifted, not true black, consistent with smartphone processing\",\n      \"color_science\": \"warm, slightly oversaturated skin tones — typical of modern smartphone auto-processing\"\n    },\n    \"color_palette\": \"warm elevated neutrals — marble whites with grey veining, walnut wood tones, brass accents, soft pink product, warm skin tones, white tank top. Cohesive and curated, no competing bold colors\"\n  },\n\n  \"negative_prompt\": {\n    \"forbidden_elements\": [\n      \"ring light reflection in eyes\",\n      \"studio backdrop\",\n      \"professional hair styling\",\n      \"heavy makeup\",\n      \"product packaging or boxes\",\n      \"text overlays or watermarks\",\n      \"other people in frame\",\n      \"brand logos on clothing\"\n    ],\n    \"forbidden_style\": [\n      \"anime\", \"CGI\", \"3D render\", \"illustration\", \"oil painting\",\n      \"uncanny valley\", \"plastic skin\", \"wax figure\", \"airbrushed\",\n      \"stock photo\", \"commercial photography\", \"catalog shot\",\n      \"overly symmetrical face\", \"perfect skin with no texture\"\n    ]\n  },\n\n  \"narrative_prompt\": \"A waist-up smartphone front camera photo of a woman in her late 20s standing in her bathroom, speaking directly to camera with a proud, excited expression — she's presenting something she built, confident smile forming, eyes bright. She has dark brown hair pulled back in a loose low bun with messy flyaway strands framing her face. Her skin is bare with realistic micro-texture — visible pores, natural oil sheen on forehead and nose, subtle warmth and flush on cheeks. She wears a plain white ribbed cotton tank top, one strap sitting loosely on her shoulder. In her right hand, held prominently at chest level with arm extended slightly toward camera in a deliberate presentation, she holds a sleek wireless women's electric razor — matte rose gold metallic body with a micro-foil head, compact and modern. The product is the focal point alongside her face. Natural morning sunlight enters from a frosted bathroom window to the left, creating soft warm directional light with gentle shadows on the right side of her face. The light catches the metallic surface of the razor with a subtle specular highlight. Behind her, slightly out of focus, is a modern curated bathroom — floating walnut vanity with brass hardware, large format white marble-look porcelain tile with subtle grey veining, edge of a round backlit mirror. On the counter: a frosted amber glass skincare bottle, a waffle-textured linen hand towel, a small ceramic tray with gold hair pins, and a sprig of dried eucalyptus in a slim white bud vase. Clean and elevated but still personal. Subtle digital grain, slightly blown-out highlights near the window, limited dynamic range consistent with smartphone sensor. 9:16 vertical aspect ratio. Social media realism — this should look like a real founder demonstrating her product in her actual bathroom, not a produced shoot.\"\n}",
