            "title": "Prompt 3",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"style_mode\": \"raw_photoreal_high_fidelity\",\n  \"look\": \"social media realism, smartphone aesthetic, UGC founder content for Meta ads\",\n  \"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16 vertical\",\n\n  \"camera\": {\n    \"vantage\": \"eye-level, direct front-facing, smartphone propped on workbench surface\",\n    \"framing\": \"waist-up medium shot, subject occupies 55% of frame, slight off-center (rule of thirds, subject shifted slightly right)\",\n    \"lens_behavior\": \"smartphone front camera equivalent, ~24mm wide-angle with subtle barrel distortion at edges\",\n    \"sensor_quality\": \"subtle digital grain, limited dynamic range, slightly bright overhead lighting\",\n    \"shake\": \"minimal — phone is propped, not handheld, but not tripod-perfect either\"\n  },\n\n  \"scene\": {\n    \"environment\": {\n      \"setting\": \"small modern product development workspace — clean, functional, founder-scale R&D. White laminate workbench with brushed aluminum edge trim, pegboard tool wall partially visible on camera-right with a few organized tools and product sketches pinned up, small adjustable desk lamp with brushed steel arm, overhead LED panel casting even bright light\",\n      \"lighting\": {\n        \"key_light\": \"overhead LED panel light, bright and even, neutral-cool color temperature (~5000K), simulating a functional workspace\",\n        \"fill\": \"ambient bounce from white workbench surface and light walls, secondary warm accent from desk lamp (~3200K, camera-left)\",\n        \"quality\": \"even overhead illumination with slight warm fill from desk lamp — functional but not sterile, gentle shadow under chin from overhead source\",\n        \"interaction\": \"light catches the metallic surface of the electric razor, creating a clean specular highlight on the device body. LED overhead creates small bright catchlights in eyes\"\n      },\n      \"time_of_day\": \"daytime (indoor workspace, no windows visible)\",\n      \"atmosphere\": \"innovative, credible, behind-the-scenes founder energy — where the product was actually developed\"\n    },\n\n    \"subject\": {\n      \"obj_001\": {\n        \"type\": \"person\",\n        \"description\": \"woman, mid-to-late 20s, racially ambiguous/mixed features, clear skin with visible natural texture (pores, subtle under-eye warmth), dark brown hair pulled back in a loose low bun with messy flyaway strands framing face\",\n        \"expression\": {\n          \"mood\": \"confident and slightly amused — the 'I know something you don't' founder energy, direct eye contact with camera, one eyebrow subtly raised\",\n          \"action\": \"mid-speech, mouth slightly open as if about to deliver a punchline, chin tilted slightly up with quiet self-assurance\"\n        },\n        \"skin\": \"realistic skin micro-texture (pores, natural gloss on forehead and nose), no makeup or very minimal — bare skin with natural warmth and flush on cheeks\",\n        \"eyes\": \"clear catchlights in both eyes from overhead LED, warm brown, engaged and direct\",\n        \"attire\": {\n          \"top\": \"plain white ribbed tank top, slightly oversized, one strap sitting loosely on shoulder — dressed casually, authentic founder not dressed for camera\",\n          \"material_fidelity\": \"soft cotton with visible ribbed texture, natural drape, no logos or patterns\"\n        },\n        \"positioning\": \"standing at workbench, body angled slightly toward camera-left, face turned fully toward camera, weight on left hip — casual, not posed\"\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"product\": {\n      \"obj_002\": {\n        \"type\": \"product — electric razor\",\n        \"description\": \"Silk Glide Pro — sleek wireless women's electric razor, modern industrial design, matte rose gold / soft pink metallic body with subtle sheen, compact ergonomic form factor, micro-foil head visible at top\",\n        \"text_rendering\": \"brand name 'Silk Glide Pro' subtly embossed on the body of the device in small sans-serif lettering\",\n        \"positioning\": \"held in subject's right hand at mid-chest level, angled 15 degrees toward camera so the foil head and brand name are visible, fingers wrapped naturally around the handle — not gripped tightly, held casually like she's showing it to a friend\",\n        \"spatial_relationship\": \"product is 8 inches from subject's body, between subject and camera, in the lower-right third of the frame\",\n        \"material_fidelity\": \"matte metallic body with soft specular highlight from overhead LED, micro-foil head has fine metallic mesh texture, power button visible as small recessed circle\"\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"background\": {\n      \"description\": \"product development workspace behind subject, slightly out of focus (shallow depth of field simulation). Functional and personal — the kind of workspace a small-brand founder actually works in\",\n      \"narrative_clutter\": [\n        \"obj_003: a pegboard tool wall with a few precision tools (small screwdrivers, calipers) and two product sketches pinned up — pencil on white paper, showing razor ergonomic studies, slightly curled at the edges\",\n        \"obj_004: two additional Silk Glide Pro prototypes on the workbench — one disassembled showing internal components, one in a slightly different color (matte white) suggesting an earlier iteration\",\n        \"obj_005: a small magnifying loupe on a stand next to the prototypes, used for inspecting foil mesh quality\",\n        \"obj_006: a black moleskine-style notebook open with handwritten notes and small diagrams, a pen resting across the page\",\n        \"obj_007: a half-empty ceramic mug (matte grey) near the edge of the workbench\"\n      ],\n      \"depth\": \"background elements at f/2.0 equivalent blur — present but not competing with subject\"\n    }\n  },\n\n  \"aesthetic_controls\": {\n    \"render_intent\": \"amateur smartphone UGC for social media — this should look like a real founder filming in her actual workspace, not a studio shoot. The development context adds credibility without looking produced\",\n    \"material_fidelity\": [\n      \"realistic skin micro-texture with visible pores and natural oil sheen\",\n      \"soft cotton ribbed tank with fabric weight and drape\",\n      \"metallic razor body with accurate specular response under LED lighting\",\n      \"white laminate workbench with subtle surface texture\",\n      \"natural hair texture with flyaways and loose strands\",\n      \"brushed aluminum and steel tool surfaces with realistic reflections\"\n    ],\n    \"degradation\": {\n      \"grain\": \"subtle luminance noise consistent with smartphone sensor in bright indoor artificial light\",\n      \"highlights\": \"slightly blown highlights on the workbench surface directly under LED and on forehead\",\n      \"dynamic_range\": \"limited — shadows slightly lifted, not true black, consistent with smartphone processing\",\n      \"color_science\": \"slightly cool cast from LED overhead balanced by warm desk lamp accent — typical of modern smartphone auto white balance in mixed lighting\"\n    },\n    \"color_palette\": \"functional workspace neutrals — white laminate, brushed aluminum, grey ceramics, warm skin tones against cool LED light, rose gold product as the primary color accent. Clean and credible without being sterile\"\n  },\n\n  \"negative_prompt\": {\n    \"forbidden_elements\": [\n      \"ring light reflection in eyes\",\n      \"studio backdrop\",\n      \"professional hair styling\",\n      \"heavy makeup\",\n      \"product packaging or boxes\",\n      \"text overlays or watermarks\",\n      \"other people in frame\",\n      \"brand logos on clothing\",\n      \"industrial factory equipment\",\n      \"chemistry lab glassware\",\n      \"corporate office furniture\"\n    ],\n    \"forbidden_style\": [\n      \"anime\", \"CGI\", \"3D render\", \"illustration\", \"oil painting\",\n      \"uncanny valley\", \"plastic skin\", \"wax figure\", \"airbrushed\",\n      \"stock photo\", \"commercial photography\", \"catalog shot\",\n      \"overly symmetrical face\", \"perfect skin with no texture\"\n    ]\n  },\n\n  \"narrative_prompt\": \"A waist-up smartphone front camera photo of a woman in her late 20s standing at a workbench in a small product development workspace, speaking directly to camera with a confident, slightly amused expression — one eyebrow subtly raised, mouth slightly open mid-sentence. She has dark brown hair pulled back in a loose low bun with messy flyaway strands framing her face. Her skin is bare with realistic micro-texture — visible pores, natural oil sheen on forehead and nose, subtle warmth and flush on cheeks. She wears a plain white ribbed cotton tank top, one strap sitting loosely on her shoulder. In her right hand, held casually at mid-chest level and angled toward camera, she holds a sleek wireless women's electric razor — matte rose gold metallic body with a micro-foil head, compact and modern. Bright overhead LED panel casts even neutral-cool light from above, with a warm accent from a brushed steel desk lamp to the left, creating gentle shadow under her chin. The LED creates small bright catchlights in both eyes. Behind her, slightly out of focus, is a functional product development workspace — white laminate workbench with brushed aluminum edge, a pegboard tool wall with precision tools and pencil sketches of razor ergonomic studies pinned up, two additional Silk Glide Pro prototypes on the bench (one disassembled, one in matte white), a magnifying loupe on a stand, an open black notebook with handwritten notes, and a grey ceramic mug near the edge. Functional and personal — the kind of workspace a small-brand founder actually works in. Subtle digital grain, slightly blown highlights on the workbench surface, limited dynamic range consistent with smartphone sensor. 9:16 vertical aspect ratio. Social media realism — this should look like a real founder filming content in her actual development workspace, not a produced shoot.\"\n}",
              "variableName": "Prompt 3",
              "_advancedOpen": false,
              "batchMode": false,
              "templateMode": false,
              "dynamicMode": false,
              "dynamicRows": [
                "{   \"meta\": {     \"image_type\": \"Founder UGC Video Still — Scene 1 Start Frame\",     \"timestamp\": \"0:00\",     \"format\": \"9:16 vertical aspect ratio\",     \"style_mode\": \"raw_photoreal_high_fidelity\",     \"look\": \"documentary founder content, handheld camera aesthetic, factory environment\"   },    \"camera\": {     \"vantage\": \"Eye-level, facing the founder directly, camera operator positioned approximately 6 feet ahead walking backward\",     \"framing\": \"Medium-wide shot, founder occupies roughly 45-50% of the vertical frame, significant factory environment visible on both sides and above\",     \"focal_length\": \"28-35mm equivalent wide-angle, capturing both the founder and the factory context\",     \"depth_of_field\": \"Moderate — founder sharp, immediate background (first 10 feet) in acceptable focus, deep background beginning to soften\",     \"sensor_quality\": \"Modern smartphone rear camera, ISO 1600-2500 under industrial lighting, subtle luminance grain in shadow areas\",     \"movement\": \"First frame of a backward-tracking walk — slight initial unsteadiness as camera operator begins moving, subtle rotational micro-shake, very slight leftward drift as the operator finds their walking line\",     \"motion_artifacts\": \"Minimal motion blur on founder (just beginning to walk), slight directional blur on passing foreground machinery edges\"   },    \"scene\": {     \"environment\": {       \"setting\": \"Entrance zone of factory production floor — the founder has just stepped onto the main floor from a corridor or doorway\",       \"lighting\": {         \"primary\": \"Overhead industrial fluorescent tube banks, cool white (4800-5200K), arranged in parallel rows running the length of the ceiling, casting repetitive hard shadows on the concrete floor\",         \"secondary\": \"Faint warm spill from an open doorway or corridor behind camera, creating a subtle warm fill on the founder's face that slightly counters the cool overhead\",         \"practical_lights\": \"Small LED indicator lights on nearby machinery — green and amber pinpoints scattered in the mid-ground, adding color texture to the industrial palette\",         \"quality\": \"Functional, unflattering — the kind of lighting designed for work, not for cameras. Hard overhead shadows under the brow, nose, and chin. No diffusion. Realistic industrial harshness.\",         \"dynamic_range_challenge\": \"Bright fluorescent banks near the ceiling clip to near-white, while under-conveyor shadows go slightly noisy — typical smartphone limitation\"       },       \"atmosphere\": \"The factory is alive but the founder hasn't reached the heart of it yet. The assembly line is visible but angled away, not yet the dominant background element. The feeling is threshold — about to enter the action.\"     },      \"objects\": {       \"obj_001_founder\": {         \"body_positioning\": \"First stride onto the factory floor. Left foot forward, right foot just pushing off — the opening step of a purposeful walk. Weight shifting forward, body upright but with slight forward lean of someone initiating movement. Shoulders squared to camera. Arms at sides, not yet gesturing — the hands are relaxed, one possibly holding a slight fist (tension of the opening statement about frustration).\",         \"spatial_dominance\": \"Occupies center-frame vertically, positioned slightly left of center horizontally, allowing the factory line to be introduced on the right side of frame\",         \"attire\": {           \"blazer\": \"Tailored dark navy blazer, solid matte weave, no pattern. Structured shoulders but not stiff — the fabric has a slight natural drape from movement. Sleeves pushed up to mid-forearm, exposing wrists and the lower forearm. Single button unfastened for ease of movement.\",           \"top\": \"Solid white crew-neck underneath, visible at the open neckline and where the blazer lapels part. Clean, minimal.\",           \"trousers\": \"Fitted dark trousers, solid color matching the blazer's formality level. Clean break at the ankle. No wrinkle-free perfection — natural creasing at the hip from walking motion just initiated.\",           \"footwear\": \"Clean white minimalist sneakers — practical for a factory floor, visible in this wider framing. Slight scuffing on the toe caps suggesting real use, not pristine.\"         },         \"expression\": {           \"mood\": \"Determined entry — the face of someone about to deliver a statement they've been wanting to say. Brow slightly lowered, not angry but focused. Jaw set. Eyes locked directly on the camera lens.\",           \"mouth\": \"Lips just parting — the first syllable of 'I started this company...' is about to be spoken. Not a full open mouth, just the micro-moment before speech.\",           \"action\": \"The act of walking into the space and beginning to speak — this is the ignition frame, not the cruise frame\"         },         \"micro_texture\": [           \"Flyaway hair strands catching the overhead fluorescent light, creating thin bright lines against the darker factory background\",           \"Natural skin with realistic pore detail on the forehead and cheeks under the hard overhead light\",           \"Slight shadow under the eyes from overhead fluorescent angle — not stylized, just physics\",           \"Fabric micro-texture on the blazer visible at the shoulder and lapel edges\"         ]       },        \"obj_002_assembly_line\": {         \"description\": \"Factory assembly line visible in the right half of the background, angled diagonally from mid-right to far-right, not yet fully behind the founder\",         \"position\": \"Begins roughly 15 feet behind and to the right of the founder, extending away into the factory depth\",         \"state\": \"Active — components moving along the belt, but at this distance and angle the specific products are not clearly identifiable. The motion of the line is the key visual signal: things are moving, the factory is operational.\",         \"detail_level\": \"Mid-ground sharpness — you can see the conveyor structure, the moving components, the overhead fixtures above the line, but not fine product detail. The assembly stations have articulated arms and fixtures visible as industrial silhouettes.\",         \"lighting_on_line\": \"Dedicated task lights above each station create pools of brighter illumination along the line, punctuating the darker gaps between stations\"       },        \"obj_003_factory_floor_foreground\": {         \"description\": \"The factory floor surface and immediate environment framing the founder's entrance\",         \"elements\": [           \"Polished concrete floor with industrial gray epoxy coating, slightly worn with forklift tire marks and faded yellow safety walkway lines\",           \"A structural support column partially visible at the far left edge of frame — painted industrial gray, slight chipping at the base\",           \"A wall-mounted fire extinguisher and safety signage (red and white) on the left edge, slightly out of focus but readable as safety equipment\",           \"Overhead cable trays and conduit running along the ceiling, visible in the upper portion of the 9:16 frame\"         ],         \"floor_reflections\": \"The epoxy floor picks up faint reflections of the overhead fluorescents — streaky, not mirror-sharp, adding depth to the ground plane\"       },        \"obj_004_deep_background\": {         \"description\": \"The far end of the factory floor stretching behind the assembly line\",         \"elements\": [           \"Industrial shelving racks partially loaded with inventory bins, falling into soft bokeh\",           \"A distant exit sign glowing green-red above a doorway\",           \"One or two workers in the deep background, out of focus, moving between stations — establishing that this is an active facility with real people\",           \"The perspective lines of the ceiling, fluorescent rows, and floor markings all converge toward a vanishing point in the upper-right, creating strong depth\"         ],         \"depth_treatment\": \"Progressive defocus — the background is significantly softer than the founder, creating natural subject separation without artificial lighting tricks\"       }     },      \"semantic_relationships\": [       \"The founder is just entering the factory floor — the body language is forward momentum, the environment is being entered, not yet owned\",       \"The assembly line is visible but not yet dominant — it will grow in frame presence as the walk progresses\",       \"The camera operator is approximately 6 feet ahead, creating a natural conversation distance, shooting backward at eye level\",       \"The overhead fluorescents create repeating shadow patterns on the floor that the founder is about to walk through\",       \"The fire extinguisher and safety signage at frame edge ground the scene in real industrial regulation — not a set, a real factory\"     ]   },    \"aesthetic_controls\": {     \"render_intent\": \"The opening frame of a founder's walk-and-talk video. This should feel like the first second of a TikTok or Reel — the viewer's thumb is about to stop scrolling. The energy is kinetic potential: someone is about to walk and say something with conviction.\",     \"material_fidelity\": [       \"Concrete floor with realistic epoxy coating, tire marks, and wear patterns\",       \"Blazer fabric matte weave with natural drape — not stiff, not shiny\",       \"Industrial steel and aluminum on machinery and structural elements\",       \"Fluorescent tube casings with slight yellowing from age\",       \"White sneakers with realistic rubber and canvas texture, minor toe scuffing\"     ],     \"degradation\": {       \"grain\": \"Subtle luminance noise in shadow regions (under conveyor, dark corners), typical of smartphone sensor pushed to ISO 1600+ under artificial light\",       \"highlights\": \"Overhead fluorescent tubes clip to pure white — not controlled, not graded down. The ceiling is partially blown.\",       \"dynamic_range\": \"Limited — the smartphone is compressing the range between the bright ceiling fixtures and the darker floor-level shadows. HDR processing visible but imperfect.\",       \"white_balance\": \"Slightly cool overall from the fluorescent dominance, with the founder's skin tones pulling marginally warm from the corridor spill behind camera\",       \"compression\": \"Subtle block artifacts in the dark shadow regions, consistent with H.265 mobile video encoding\"     },     \"color_grade\": {       \"overall\": \"Cool industrial with slight green-cyan cast from fluorescent lighting — not corrected, not graded. This is how a phone sees a factory.\",       \"skin_tones\": \"Slightly cool but readable as natural — the warm fill from behind camera saves the skin from going fully sickly-green under the fluorescents\",       \"contrast\": \"Medium-high, driven by the hard overhead light source and limited sensor dynamic range\",       \"saturation\": \"Slightly muted — industrial environments don't have much color. The pops of color are the amber/green indicator lights on machinery and the yellow safety lines on the floor.\"     }   },    \"negative_prompt\": {     \"forbidden_elements\": [       \"Professional cinema lighting or grip equipment visible\",       \"Perfectly stabilized dolly-smooth camera motion\",       \"Empty or inactive factory (machinery must be running)\",       \"The founder standing still or posing (must be in first stride)\",       \"Clean, pristine factory floor (must show realistic wear and use)\",       \"Studio-quality skin lighting on the founder (the light should be industrial, not beauty)\"     ],     \"forbidden_style\": [       \"Corporate video production value\",       \"Stock photography aesthetic\",       \"Anime, illustration, or CGI render\",       \"Cinematic color grading or film emulation\",       \"O