            "title": "Prompt 6",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"scene\": 4,\n  \"title\": \"THE DEMO + PAYOFF\",\n  \"timing\": \"0:24-0:32\",\n  \"duration\": \"8s\",\n  \"reference_frame\": \"scene-03-04-image-start.json (bathroom demo)\",\n  \"profile\": \"default (modified: 165 WPM, high energy)\",\n  \"script_segment\": \"no nicks, no bumps, no irritation. Smooth skin. Every single time.\",\n  \"word_count\": 11,\n  \"speech_duration\": \"~4.0s\",\n  \"visual_beat\": \"~4.0s demo visuals + results payoff\",\n\n  \"visual\": \"Static camera shot. Fixed angle. She completes the demo glide on her forearm — smooth stroke. On 'no nicks, no bumps, no irritation' she gestures with her free hand, dismissing each one — natural hand movements, not choreographed. After the list, her energy settles. On 'Smooth skin' she runs her fingertips over the area she just shaved — feeling the result. Genuine satisfied expression. On 'Every single time' she looks at camera with quiet confidence and a small nod. Holds the look.\",\n\n  \"audio\": \"DIALOGUE: \\\"no nicks, no bumps, no irritation. Smooth skin. Every single time.\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. 'No nicks, no bumps, no irritation' is quick and confident — ticking off a list. Then the pace drops for 'Smooth skin' — warmer, satisfied. 'Every single time' is calm and sure. The energy goes from listing to savoring. General American accent.\",\n\n  \"negative_prompt\": \"camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\",\n\n  \"prompt\": \"Static camera shot. Fixed angle. She completes a demo glide on her forearm. On 'no nicks, no bumps, no irritation' she gestures with her free hand, naturally dismissing each one. After the list, energy settles. On 'Smooth skin' she runs fingertips over the shaved area, genuine satisfied expression. On 'Every single time' she looks at camera with quiet confidence, small nod. Holds the look.\\n\\nDIALOGUE: \\\"no nicks, no bumps, no irritation. Smooth skin. Every single time.\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. 'No nicks, no bumps, no irritation' is quick and confident, ticking off a list. Then pace drops for 'Smooth skin' — warmer, satisfied. 'Every single time' calm and sure. General American accent.\\n\\nNegative prompt: camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\"\n}",
