            "title": "Prompt 5",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"scene\": 5,\n  \"title\": \"THE CLOSE\",\n  \"timing\": \"0:32-0:40\",\n  \"duration\": \"8s\",\n  \"reference_frame\": \"scene-01-02-05-image-start.json (lab/development workspace — bookend with Scene 1)\",\n  \"profile\": \"default (modified: 165 WPM, high energy)\",\n  \"script_segment\": \"I made this for every woman who's been let down by her razor. Link's right here — try it yourself.\",\n  \"word_count\": 19,\n  \"speech_duration\": \"~6.9s\",\n  \"visual_beat\": \"~1.1s held final expression\",\n\n  \"visual\": \"Static camera shot. Front-facing, same framing as Scene 1. She holds the Silk Glide Pro at chest level. On 'I made this' she briefly touches her chest — a natural self-referential gesture. On 'every woman' her hand opens toward camera. On 'who's been let down' her expression shows genuine understanding — she's been there. On 'Link's right here' she glances down briefly, then back to camera. On 'try it yourself' she points at camera with a confident smile. Holds the smile for the last second.\",\n\n  \"audio\": \"DIALOGUE: \\\"I made this for every woman who's been let down by her razor. Link's right here — try it yourself.\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. Warm and direct — this is the personal close. 'I made this' has pride. 'Every woman who's been let down' is genuine, not preachy. 'Link's right here' is casual. 'Try it yourself' is an invitation with confidence. General American accent.\",\n\n  \"negative_prompt\": \"camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\",\n\n  \"prompt\": \"Static camera shot. Front-facing, same framing as Scene 1. She holds the Silk Glide Pro at chest level. On 'I made this' she briefly touches her chest. On 'every woman' her hand opens toward camera. On 'who's been let down' her expression shows genuine understanding. On 'Link's right here' she glances down briefly, then back to camera. On 'try it yourself' she points at camera with a confident smile. Holds the smile.\\n\\nDIALOGUE: \\\"I made this for every woman who's been let down by her razor. Link's right here — try it yourself.\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. Warm and direct. 'I made this' has pride. 'Every woman who's been let down' is genuine. 'Link's right here' casual. 'Try it yourself' an invitation with confidence. General American accent.\\n\\nNegative prompt: camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\"\n}",
