            "title": "Prompt 7",
            "properties": {
              "text": "{\n  \"scene\": 3,\n  \"title\": \"THE REVEAL + DEMO START\",\n  \"timing\": \"0:16-0:24\",\n  \"duration\": \"8s\",\n  \"reference_frame\": \"scene-03-04-image-start.json (bathroom demo)\",\n  \"profile\": \"default (modified: 165 WPM, high energy)\",\n  \"script_segment\": \"Meet Silk Glide Pro. Wireless. Designed for women's skin. Glides right over curves —\",\n  \"word_count\": 13,\n  \"speech_duration\": \"~4.7s\",\n  \"visual_beat\": \"~3.3s product reveal + demo start\",\n\n  \"visual\": \"Static camera shot. Front-facing angle. She raises the Silk Glide Pro into frame with her right hand — proud but not over-the-top, like showing a friend something she made. On 'Wireless' she gives it a casual turn in her hand to show there's no cord. On 'Designed for women's skin' she touches her own forearm briefly. On 'Glides right over curves' she brings the razor toward her forearm and starts a slow demo glide. Scene ends mid-demonstration — she's focused on what she's doing, confident in the result.\",\n\n  \"audio\": \"DIALOGUE: \\\"Meet Silk Glide Pro. Wireless. Designed for women's skin. Glides right over curves —\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. Proud and direct — she's introducing something she built. 'Meet Silk Glide Pro' is clear and deliberate. 'Wireless' is punchy, standalone. 'Designed for women's skin' is warmer. 'Glides right over curves' flows naturally, trailing off as she starts the demo. General American accent.\",\n\n  \"negative_prompt\": \"camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\",\n\n  \"prompt\": \"Static camera shot. Front-facing angle. She raises the Silk Glide Pro into frame with her right hand — proud but natural, like showing a friend something she made. On 'Wireless' she turns it casually to show no cord. On 'Designed for women's skin' she touches her own forearm. On 'Glides right over curves' she brings the razor toward her forearm and starts a slow demo glide. Scene ends mid-demonstration.\\n\\nDIALOGUE: \\\"Meet Silk Glide Pro. Wireless. Designed for women's skin. Glides right over curves —\\\"\\n\\nDELIVERY: 165 WPM. Proud and direct. 'Meet Silk Glide Pro' is clear and deliberate. 'Wireless' punchy. 'Designed for women's skin' warmer. 'Glides right over curves' flows naturally, trailing off into the demo. General American accent.\\n\\nNegative prompt: camera movement, shaky cam, zooming, panning, dolly shots, tracking shots, handheld movement, monotone voice, flat affect, robotic speech, whispered speech, professional narrator voice, cartoonish eyes, bug eyes, exaggerated expressions, sound effects, whooshes, background music, ambient noise, fake excitement, infomercial style, shouting\"\n}",
